Sentencas: Anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells with a thin him of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) as the electrolyte were fabricated.
Titulo: A high performance, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell operating on direct alcohol

Sentencas: The cells were operated directly on pure methanol and on an equivolume mixture of ethanol and water over a range of temperatures.
Titulo: A high performance, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell operating on direct alcohol

Sentencas: Power density achieved with methanol was between 0.6 W/cm(2) at 650 degreesC and 1.3 W/cm(2) at 800 degreesC. and with ethanol + water between 0.3 W/cm(2) at 650 degreesC and 0.8 W/cm(2) at 800 degreesC. Results were compared with tests on humidified hydrogen us a fuel.
Titulo: A high performance, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell operating on direct alcohol

Sentencas: No carbon deposition on the Ni-YSZ anode was observed with either methanol or an equivolume solution of ethanol and water as fuels.
Titulo: A high performance, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell operating on direct alcohol

Sentencas: Differences in performance with different fuels were attributed to differences in anode polarization.
Titulo: A high performance, anode-supported solid oxide fuel cell operating on direct alcohol
